title: Classic Jhin vs Highnoon Jhin
body:
hi there is a bug with Jhin E if on the enemy team is a Jhin with Highnoon skin

Place a trap
go away for a while 
let enemy jhin / minions hit your trap
and bom
the animation of classic jhin traps is themed as Highnoon skin bombs
this always happen to me

replies.body:
Hiya TN Leymo! 

Thanks for the report! This appears to be audio theft. It's a known issue and the team is looking into it. :)
